<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<% include ../partials/head.ejs %>

  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="body-wrapper">
        <% include ../partials/nav.ejs %>
          <% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
            <% results.forEach(function(r) { %>
              <div class="upgrade-content">
                <div class="content-wrapper">
                  <p class="large">Your Sandbox
                    <strong>
                      <%= r.org_id  %>
                    </strong> is a
                    <%= r.org_type  %> Instance,
                      <br/>on
                      <%= r.external_rel_name  %>
                  </p>
                  
                  <h3>What would you like information on?</h3>
                  <p class="upgrade-option" id="upgrade">Upgrade to Winter '19
                    <br />by Sep 8, 2018</p>
                  <div class="component upgrade-info" id="upgrade">
                    <% if (r.org_type == "PREVIEW") {  %>
                      <p>
                        <strong>No action is needed</strong> as your Sandbox is already on a Preview Instance</p>
                      <p>If you need to refresh for other reasons, do so well in advance of 11:59pm PT on Sep 7, 2018 (7:59
                        UTC on Sep 8, 2018) to make sure your Sandbox completes before the deadline. If you refresh after
                        the deadline or your Sandbox doesn't complete in time, it will be built on a Non-Preview Instance.</p>

                      <% } %>
                        <% if (r.org_type == "NON-PREVIEW") { %>
                          <p>To get the preview, we require you to refresh to a Sandbox instance that will be upgraded early
                            to Winter '19.
                          </p>

                          <p>
                            <strong>Please refresh well in advance of 11:59p.m. PT on Sep 7, 2018 (07:59 UTC on Sep 8, 2018)</strong>.
                            If you refresh after the deadline or your Sandbox doesn't complete in time, it will be built
                            on a Non-Preview instance.
                          </p>

                          <% } %>
                  </div>
                  <p class="upgrade-option" id="stay">Stay on Summer '18
                    <br />until Oct 13, 2018</p>
                  <div class="component upgrade-info" id="stay">
                    <% if (r.org_type == "PREVIEW") { %>
                      <p>To stay on Summer '18, we require you to refresh to a Non-Preview Sandbox Instance.</p>
                      <p>
                        <strong>Please wait and refresh after 12:00am PT on Sep 8, 2018 (8:00 UTC on Sep 8, 2018).</strong> If you
                        refresh before this date, your Sandbox may be built on a Preview Instance.</p>

                      <% } %>
                        <% if (r.org_type == "NON-PREVIEW") { %>
                          <p>
                            <strong>No action is needed</strong> as your Sandbox is already on a Non-Preview Instance</p>
                          <p>If you need to refresh for other reasons, please wait and refresh after 12:00 a.m. PT on Sep 8,
                            2018 (8:00 UTC on Sep 8, 2018) to remain on a Non-Preview Instance.</p>

                          <% } %>
                  </div>
                  <p class="large">
                    <strong>Note: </strong> All production and sandbox environments will be upgraded<br />to Winter â€˜18 by Oct 13, 2018.</p>
                  <% }); %>
                
                    <div class="component">
                      <div class="divider"></div>
                      <% include ../partials/helpful-links.ejs %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% include ../partials/footer.ejs %>
        <% include ../partials/script_section.ejs %>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>